00:02:07.369 --> 00:02:08.390
So thatís half way.

00:02:08.390 --> 00:02:10.470
The bottom of the tree would be down at about
the floor.

00:02:10.470 --> 00:02:12.930
Thatís the house.

00:02:12.930 --> 00:02:15.620
