I was a young child there was a guy named,

00:03:26.190 --> 00:03:30.610
my father worked at this placed called The
Institute for Advanced Study in Princeton,

00:03:30.610 --> 00:03:33.920
but not part of the university, my mother
worked there too.

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:38.340
