boring things.

00:03:38.340 --> 00:03:42.380
They worked on pencil and paper and maybe
they wrote on the chalkboard and erased it

00:03:42.380 --> 00:03:43.380
the next day.

00:03:43.380 --> 00:03:49.290
But Johnny Von Neumann had a building out
back where he was building a computer.

00:03:49.290 --> 00:03:55.540
And it was not the first computer, itís impossible
to get the people, you know, discussing and

00:03:55.540 --> 00:04:00.000
trying to sell this book, to not say, ìGeorgeís
book is about the first computer.î Itís

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:01.000
not the first computer.

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:03.590
There were many, many computers before this
computer.

00:04:03.590 --> 00:04:10.080
