00:05:04.080 --> 00:05:08.629
far ahead of its time but still in print.

00:05:08.629 --> 00:05:12.949
And looks at this very large description of
where did this digital universe come from

00:05:12.949 --> 00:05:14.180
on the long side?

00:05:14.180 --> 00:05:18.979
In this book, I take it back to Thomas Hobbes
in the 17th century.

00:05:18.979 --> 00:05:25.890
One of the people who appreciated this book
