the doors to the history of advanced study

00:05:55.520 --> 00:06:00.889
where there archives had been kept closed
to outside researchers since 1946.

00:06:00.889 --> 00:06:06.729
And I happened to come, be with Charles when
he came to Google for the first time.

00:06:06.729 --> 00:06:09.389
We were riding a bus together to an event
here.

00:06:09.389 --> 00:06:13.749
