00:06:29.410 --> 00:06:33.449
[Laughter]
&gt;&gt;George Dyson: And you were only 2 years

00:06:33.449 --> 00:06:36.759
old.

00:06:36.759 --> 00:06:43.330
So Charles sent me on this path ten years
