00:07:17.020 --> 00:07:21.569
[Laughter]
&gt;&gt;George Dyson: All of John Von Neumannís

00:07:21.569 --> 00:07:26.339
papers went the library of Congress, but this
filing cabinet didnít and his daughter said,

00:07:26.339 --> 00:07:30.619
you know, ìYou should come to Ann Arbor,
