00:07:30.619 --> 00:07:31.619
had looked.

00:07:31.619 --> 00:07:36.770
I opened, and to me as a historian, the most
interesting, sort of, dark period of technology

00:07:36.770 --> 00:07:43.469
history is like between 1937, just before
World War II and Sputnik.

00:07:43.469 --> 00:07:46.129
